Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:02.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.29,0:00:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the start of Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all\nthe shards of the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:08.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'll destroy Naraku with my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naraku slays Kikyo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.37,0:00:14.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then sends his new infant incarnation\nto attack the darkness in our hearts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:16.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha has gone in\nsearch of Kikyo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:18.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and is unable to come\nto save me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.71,0:00:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time for a Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:06.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Help me, Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:11.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is searching\nfor Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha won't come to\nsave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:29.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've grasped the darkness\nin your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:33.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now hold me tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:37.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let our souls unite and...\nbecome my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:45.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Find peace in death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:01.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:12.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hard work to fight\nwithout killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.68,0:03:15.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's easier to deal with demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't good.\NIt's taking too much time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:25.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome, be safe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph!\NThey're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Furthermore, they don't intend to kill\nthe castle's soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're easygoing, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But soon, they'll want to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all, the soldiers are intent\non killing the monk and his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The evil will of the soldiers\nwill become contagious
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and soon, the humans will\nkill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The human heart is weak.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hatred is easily bred.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This girl is no different...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.55,0:04:20.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I followed the directions\nof that old priest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and came to the river's edge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:25.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't catch Kikyo's scent\naround here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And there isn't a villager around\nwho's seen a priestess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:39.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:41.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're gone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:51.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I think I eluded them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Inuyasha's nowhere\nto be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Kirara and I have\nbecome separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have any other\noptions {\i1}left....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.36,0:05:03.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess I have to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:11.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? Kagome was taken\naway to a castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}While I searched for Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:35.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}a trap?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, let's hurry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me!\NOh let me be in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not falter! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's over for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,P-Please save us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:04.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry Sango, if I use my Wind\NTunnel, we could escape alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:08.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't want to live at\nthe expense of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:15.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must go and save Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:20.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Absolutely!\NIt's not in my nature to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:25.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku! Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:34.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:36.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.89,0:06:43.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.73,0:06:47.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of here, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:55.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're mere humans...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This smell... Could it be.?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, Kagome is inside the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:07.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! This is Kagura's smell!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This priest...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said that Kikyo was alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:24.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It WAS a trap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:26.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!\NI'm too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:51.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it isn't Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:07:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? A Sacred Jewel shard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Implant that tainted Sacred Jewel\nshard into Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:08.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Kagome will be\ncompletely under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My mission is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:13.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once this is over, I shall go\ninto hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... With this, Kagome will\nbecome Naraku's slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same fate as Kohaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kohaku...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This impure light...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You intend to place that shard\nin me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:36.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:39.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! I-I can't move!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it because this baby...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}has a grasp upon my soul?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to break free...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:49.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to free myself\nfrom him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:52.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:54.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's a stubborn one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come save me... lnuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:02.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, don't you, that\nhe won't come to save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rather than you, Inuyasha\nhas chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:19.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!\NI'm such an idiot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is no time to hesitate!\NHurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm making the same mistake again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost Kikyo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought I was the only one hurting...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and acted selfishly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I'm about to lose\nanother precious person...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait until I get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:23.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think hard, Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:31.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When you learned that\NKikyo had died...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:34.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,didn't you actually feel happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:37.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The woman who came between\nyou was gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:40.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the moment Inuyasha heard\nthat Kikyo was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he went after her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:46.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whether she is dead or alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:49.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's heart belongs\nto Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:54.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bitter towards Inuyasha?\NDon't you hate Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:11:00.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay to hate.\NYou are not wrong to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:03.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fill your heart with hatred\nonce more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.19,0:11:06.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And let me grasp your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:11.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So she gave in...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:36.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate Inuyasha...?\NI loathe Kikyo...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.16,0:11:39.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:50.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NShe repelled the shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:54.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm... Here's something even\nthis kid can't do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:55.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:00.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She spoke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}M- My suggestive powers...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}have no effect on this girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:07.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What you're saying is\nall wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:14.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though, rationally, I can accept\nthat Inuyasha can't forget Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still feel jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:17.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:25.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Resenting Inuyasha...\NAnd being jealous of Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:28.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are feelings that\nany human would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And they're not used to curse people\nlike you tell me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There have been numerous times\nwhen Inuyasha left my side
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:42.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because he understood\nhow difficult it was for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There were times when I did\nwish that Kikyo was {\i1}gone....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I felt bad that I even harbored\nsuch thoughts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all these feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it all means {\i1}that....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm in love with Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:08.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You came for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No wonder Naraku\ncan't stand that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:17.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.75,0:13:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did you do\nto Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I just tugged at her\nsoul a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:27.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since you can't seem to\nget over Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:30.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there's a bit of darkness\nin that girl's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One more step, and I would have\nbroken her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura! Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:50.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The monk and the Demon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many soldiers did\nyou kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:14:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This infant... Was he manipulating\nthe castle's soldiers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hate to disappoint you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but we don't kill\nunnecessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This infant...\nthe ghastly color of his skin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he an incarnation created from\nthe clumps of flesh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}which Naraku\nwas producing at Mt. Hakurei?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:18.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you Naraku's human heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku hid himself away\nat Mt. Hakurei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:26.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to create a more\npowerful body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:27.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.69,0:14:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to cast away his human heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:33.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku said he cut away his\nhuman heart
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:35.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,which continued to yearn for Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to get rid of Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is the human heart which\nhad feelings for Kikyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.81,0:14:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Toying with people's hearts\nin a dastardly {\i1}way....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:57.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Perhaps I am indeed the human\nheart which Naraku once possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can clearly see into a person's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Their weaknesses\nand frailties.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know just what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:09.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,in order to make one suffer,\nfeel sorrow or hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see it all so clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:19.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If there is one feeling that\NI did NOT inherit from Naraku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the anguish of yearning\nfor Kikyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where do you think that\nfeeling went?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The disgusting clumps of flesh you\nsaw at Mt. Hakurei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:36.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the abandoned heart?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:41.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am free of suffering and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:47.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you're just a monster created\nfrom Naraku's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,twisted and grotesque!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all I need to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die!\NWind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:07.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This kid...\NCan he put up a barrier?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:09.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, he's one creepy brat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-My Wind Scar is being sucked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no!\NEveryone, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That kid...\NHe countered the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't think this is over.\NI'll come to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:50.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:52.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you touch Kagome again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That girl is the only one,\nsince Kikyo is gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:01.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,who can see the Sacred Jewel shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.05,0:17:02.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:05.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Very, very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:11.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Once Kagome's eyes become mine,\nthe Sacred Jewel will become whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:14.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A Sacred Jewel filled\nwith hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:19.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if Kagome would do\nanything for Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are countless ways\nto corrupt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:30.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0} As long as you cannot\nforget Kikyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.69,0:17:46.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome... I'm sorry\NI left you all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:51.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll never let you fall into\NNaraku's hands again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Never...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}will I let you suffer\nlike Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?\NYou look listless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet! I need to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome's soul is\nstronger than I expected.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used up too much energy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this kid?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did his struggle with Kagome\ntire him out?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He may be Naraku's\ninfant incarnation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's not all-powerful, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.78,0:20:28.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say no more, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:37.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo was forced\nto return to the living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:44.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And while here, her soul\nonly suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I couldn't save Kikyo's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For a second time, she was killed\nby that bastard Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:20:59.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sister Kikyo's soul has faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She won't need to suffer anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.12,0:21:03.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:06.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So Inuyasha, you need not\nsuffer anymore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.26,0:21:11.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, my sister is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:13.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.56,0:21:19.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I would have liked to bury her\nbones here at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:27.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will Kagome be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:30.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She continues to sleep\neven after returning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:36.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She'll be fine. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I {\i1}see....{\i0}\NInuyasha, you did come for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.28,0:22:02.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay?\NTake it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:07.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, I'm sorry\nabout what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:10.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wasn't with you {\i1}and....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:13.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:16.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I let you fall into\nharm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:22.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Any later and I would've\nlost Kagome, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:30.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, if you hear news of Kikyo's\nwhereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:31.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you'll go off to look for her\nagain, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:35.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, I won't!\NI won't ever leave you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:38.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the type who'd go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:43.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How long do you think\NI've known you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:45.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You would go.\NNo doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:50.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when you do go,\NI'll be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.13,0:22:52.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's to be expected, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.86,0:22:56.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:03.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you're mad, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:06.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I am, {\i1}but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:14.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha will never\nforget Kikyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I still love him...\NSo there's nothing I can do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:27.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks, Kagome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:39.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I came back to the present hoping\nto get some serious studying done!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.01,0:23:40.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Chorus!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:41.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.78,0:23:43.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cooking demonstration?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.38,0:23:45.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why not?\NIt's a cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you didn't help at\nall with the preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so you're on standby\nfor everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.52,0:23:52.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.19,0:23:54.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if you mess up,\nyou'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.22,0:23:59.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Don't Boil It!\NThe Terrifying Dried-Up Demon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:01.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd rather fight a demon\nfrom the Feudal Era!
